project NotifyActiveUsers

task Notify
    goal
        Every active user receives exactly one email.
    input
        users
    constraint
        No duplicate emails per user.
        Retry failures up to 3 times.
        Parallel execution allowed.
        Log every failure.
    success
        100% delivery to active users.
    test
        Inactive users are not notified.
        A transient failure is retried.
        A permanent failure is logged.
